skdetail:
Flash Briefing Skill
This skill contains: dynamic content.
des: If you were wondering how to use all of the products you've accumulated under your sink then wonder no more. With this skill you will hear right from the professional stylist on how to get the most out of your products. We'll share tips, ingredient info, orgin stories, and ways to use the products that help you get the most bang for your buck. You'll also be able to discover new products that we love and get exclusive access to try them.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
